and returned them totally safe.

00:15:32.522 --> 00:15:34.730 align:middle line:84%
And she said that our family
has a history of working

00:15:34.730 --> 00:15:36.890 align:middle line:84%
with these people
and that she just

00:15:36.890 --> 00:15:39.575 align:middle line:84%
wanted to let me know this
before she left this Earth.

00:15:39.575 --> 00:15:42.273 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK, let's talk
about the megalithic site

00:15:42.273 --> 00:15:43.940 align:middle line:84%
