family helped build it.

00:15:43.940 --> 00:15:45.710 align:middle line:84%
And so if it's megalithic,
link that means your family's

00:15:45.710 --> 00:15:47.720 align:middle line:84%
been doing this for many,
many thousands of years.

00:15:47.720 --> 00:15:47.890 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Right.

00:15:47.890 --> 00:15:50.660 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So they're somehow in
companionship, collaboration,

00:15:50.660 --> 00:15:54.250 align:middle line:84%
or maybe even genetically
tied with the people that

00:15:54.250 --> 00:15:55.050 align:middle line:90%
have been coming?

00:15:55.050 --> 00:15:57.800 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: Yeah, something
really interesting.

00:15:57.800 --> 00:16:01.550 align:middle line:84%
Only 15% of the world have
Rh-negative blood, and my mom,

00:16:01.550 --> 00:16:05.240 align:middle line:84%
