00:16:05.240 --> 00:16:07.270 align:middle line:84%
And just in one family,
that's too close--

00:16:07.270 --> 00:16:09.650 align:middle line:84%
that's so close to
be a coincidence.

00:16:09.650 --> 00:16:11.690 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, just
so everybody knows what

00:16:11.690 --> 00:16:15.620 align:middle line:84%
you're talking about here, that
is often associated with alien

00:16:15.620 --> 00:16:18.518 align:middle line:84%
DNA or not-of-this-Earth DNA,
however you want to call it.

00:16:18.518 --> 00:16:19.560 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Right, correct.

00:16:19.560 --> 00:16:20.930 align:middle line:90%
That's what biologists say.

00:16:20.930 --> 00:16:23.450 align:middle line:84%
I have to donate my own
blood to my local plasma bank

00:16:23.450 --> 00:16:26.030 align:middle line:84%
