call in case something happens

00:16:26.030 --> 00:16:27.710 align:middle line:84%
to me, they don't
have to go digging

00:16:27.710 --> 00:16:28.460 align:middle line:84%
and figuring out
where they're going

00:16:28.460 --> 00:16:29.668 align:middle line:90%
to get blood for transfusion.

00:16:29.668 --> 00:16:30.980 align:middle line:90%
I can transfuse my own self.

00:16:30.980 --> 00:16:34.130 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Are you an O,
AB, or some combination?

00:16:34.130 --> 00:16:39.425 align:middle line:10%
Are you O, A, or AB, B, or AB
in your dominant blood type?

00:16:39.425 --> 00:16:40.270 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: O, yeah.

00:16:40.270 --> 00:16:41.070 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:16:41.070 --> 00:16:45.650 align:middle line:10%
