indication you're

00:17:20.655 --> 00:17:24.730 align:middle line:84%
coming from a different genetic
bloodline than a normal human's

00:17:24.730 --> 00:17:25.530 align:middle line:90%
person.

00:17:25.530 --> 00:17:26.697 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Yeah, interesting.

00:17:26.697 --> 00:17:32.510 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK so did your mother
