00:18:59.900 --> 00:19:03.350 align:middle line:84%
Everybody knew him for his
capability and ability to fish.

00:19:03.350 --> 00:19:05.960 align:middle line:84%
He literally fed entire
neighborhoods with fish.

00:19:05.960 --> 00:19:07.580 align:middle line:84%
He would go out
and fish and fish,

00:19:07.580 --> 00:19:10.140 align:middle line:84%
and he would bring
home the most--

00:19:10.140 --> 00:19:11.640 align:middle line:84%
my first day home
from the hospital.

00:19:11.640 --> 00:19:13.755 align:middle line:90%
I remember being there.

00:19:13.755 --> 00:19:14.555 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Hospital?

00:19:14.555 --> 00:19:16.610 align:middle line:10%
>>CARSON: My first day
home from being born, yeah.

00:19:16.610 --> 00:19:17.315 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: You remember?

00:19:17.315 --> 00:19:18.740 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: I remember the
first day they brought me

00:19:18.740 --> 00:19:19.603 align:middle line:90%
to the house, yeah.

00:19:19.603 --> 00:19:22.020 align:middle line:84%
And I told them what they fed
me and everybody went crazy.

00:19:22.020 --> 00:19:22.823 align:middle line:90%
It was fish.

00:19:22.823 --> 00:19:24.240 align:middle line:84%
My grandmother
gave me table food.

00:19:24.240 --> 00:19:25.615 align:middle line:84%
She gave me some
of the bluefish,

00:19:25.615 --> 00:19:28.310 align:middle line:84%
which actually became my
favorite fish until I stopped

00:19:28.310 --> 00:19:29.810 align:middle line:90%
eating fish, and that's--

00:19:29.810 --> 00:19:31.250 align:middle line:90%
my grandfather caught that fish.

00:19:31.250 --> 00:19:32.345 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: You're a vegan today?

00:19:32.345 --> 00:19:33.080 align:middle line:10%
>>CARSON: Yes.

00:19:33.080 --> 00:19:34.290 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yes, that's
what I thought.

00:19:34.290 --> 00:19:35.090 align:middle line:90%
I recall.

00:19:35.090 --> 00:19:36.577 align:middle line:90%
And we'll talk about that, too.

00:19:36.577 --> 00:19:37.827 align:middle line:90%
I'm writing little notes here.

00:19:37.827 --> 00:19:38.910 align:middle line:90%
Vegan.

00:19:38.910 --> 00:19:39.710 align:middle line:90%
OK.

00:19:39.710 --> 00:19:44.030 align:middle line:84%
All right, there are so many
things to ask at this point.

00:19:44.030 --> 00:19:47.030 align:middle line:84%
And I do want to get back to
this notion of having knowledge

00:19:47.030 --> 00:19:49.610 align:middle line:84%
