00:20:20.210 --> 00:20:21.377 align:middle line:10%
An American and German team?

00:20:21.377 --> 00:20:22.177 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Yeah.

00:20:22.177 --> 00:20:23.870 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: For a part
of his, I recall,

00:20:23.870 --> 00:20:26.657 align:middle line:84%
restoration of the Great
Pyramid or the Sphinx?

00:20:26.657 --> 00:20:28.490 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: The Great
Pyramids and the Sphinx.

00:20:28.490 --> 00:20:28.745 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: OK.

00:20:28.745 --> 00:20:30.260 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: Both
needed restoration.

00:20:30.260 --> 00:20:32.600 align:middle line:84%
Some areas of the Great
Pyramid on one of the corners

00:20:32.600 --> 00:20:35.000 align:middle line:84%
