and the Great Sphinx,

00:20:35.000 --> 00:20:36.417 align:middle line:84%
from time to time,
it always needs

00:20:36.417 --> 00:20:39.290 align:middle line:84%
to be fixed because
of weathering

00:20:39.290 --> 00:20:42.140 align:middle line:84%
patterns and everything
else and deterioration.

00:20:42.140 --> 00:20:44.412 align:middle line:84%
So I thought it was so
interesting like, you know--

00:20:44.412 --> 00:20:45.870 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Why are
they calling him?

00:20:45.870 --> 00:20:47.330 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Yeah, exactly.

00:20:47.330 --> 00:20:50.210 align:middle line:84%
I mean, this is like
just an amazing thing.

00:20:50.210 --> 00:20:52.370 align:middle line:84%
And it's like-- it's
well documented.

00:20:52.370 --> 00:20:53.690 align:middle line:84%
So it's not even-- you
