again.

00:21:05.750 --> 00:21:08.810 align:middle line:84%
If their understanding was
their family history was

00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:13.090 align:middle line:84%
as a part of the architectural
team of these megalithic sites

00:21:13.090 --> 00:21:15.320 align:middle line:84%
and that had been passed
down, did the women

00:21:15.320 --> 00:21:18.230 align:middle line:84%
or the men in your
