hospital, he was alive.

00:22:20.130 --> 00:22:21.950 align:middle line:90%
He had a broken collarbone.

00:22:21.950 --> 00:22:24.398 align:middle line:84%
All the blood that
was on him wasn't his.

00:22:24.398 --> 00:22:25.940 align:middle line:84%
And this is another
well-documented--

00:22:25.940 --> 00:22:27.857 align:middle line:84%
can be searched, researched,
can be looked up,

00:22:27.857 --> 00:22:29.210 align:middle line:90%
well-documented event.

