00:47:17.590 --> 00:47:20.650 align:middle line:84%
I think it has value to
know your personal history.

00:47:20.650 --> 00:47:24.145 align:middle line:84%
And I've taken people
through-- quite a few people

00:47:24.145 --> 00:47:25.395 align:middle line:90%
