00:47:25.395 --> 00:47:26.195 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Oh, wow.

00:47:26.195 --> 00:47:29.350 align:middle line:10%
>>REGINA: And in doing
so, the main thing

00:47:29.350 --> 00:47:32.590 align:middle line:10%
is people either think
