00:47:32.590 --> 00:47:37.510 align:middle line:10%
and that I'm going to be lying
to myself, or I was nothing.

00:47:37.510 --> 00:47:40.570 align:middle line:84%
I mean, they have these fears
and preconceptions going in.

00:47:40.570 --> 00:47:43.900 align:middle line:84%
And I say, you know, don't worry
about any of those details.

00:47:43.900 --> 00:47:47.280 align:middle line:84%
You can make up a fantabulous
story if you want to even.

00:47:47.280 --> 00:47:49.440 align:middle line:84%
But the feeling that
you bring forth inside

00:47:49.440 --> 00:47:52.260 align:middle line:84%
is the junk that's buried
in the subconscious.

00:47:52.260 --> 00:47:54.630 align:middle line:84%
And that's what's
actually affecting you

00:47:54.630 --> 00:47:56.040 align:middle line:90%
in your current incarnation.

00:47:56.040 --> 00:47:56.410 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Yeah.

00:47:56.410 --> 00:47:57.450 align:middle line:90%
Yeah, that's like shadow work.

00:47:57.450 --> 00:47:58.130 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:47:58.130 --> 00:47:58.320 align:middle line:90%
>>CARSON: Yeah.

00:47:58.320 --> 00:48:00.070 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So you're
bringing that through.

00:48:00.070 --> 00:48:04.080 align:middle line:10%
So if you're in a situation such
as from the lineage of slavery

00:48:04.080 --> 00:48:05.860 align:middle line:10%
and that's been
reinforced, reinforced,

00:48:05.860 --> 00:48:08.430 align:middle line:10%
almost up till present,
which it really has--

00:48:08.430 --> 00:48:10.420 align:middle line:10%
look at what happened
to your father--

00:48:10.420 --> 00:48:12.930 align:middle line:10%
>>CARSON: Mm-hmm, yeah, that
was the second time that he

00:48:12.930 --> 00:48:14.160 align:middle line:10%
had been beaten by cops.

00:48:14.160 --> 00:48:17.203 align:middle line:84%
The first time, I witnessed
it in Opa-locka, Florida.

00:48:17.203 --> 00:48:18.870 align:middle line:84%
We went to go pay the
rent for the house

00:48:18.870 --> 00:48:21.690 align:middle line:84%
that we were living in, at this
lady who owned a dry cleaner.

00:48:21.690 --> 00:48:24.643 align:middle line:84%
And unfortunately, six
cops came, slammed him

00:48:24.643 --> 00:48:26.310 align:middle line:84%
to the ground, put
shotguns to his head,

00:48:26.310 --> 00:48:27.720 align:middle line:84%
hit him with the
butt of the gun.

00:48:27.720 --> 00:48:28.710 align:middle line:84%
Me and my brother
were screaming.

00:48:28.710 --> 00:48:29.585 align:middle line:90%
My mom was screaming.

00:48:29.585 --> 00:48:32.190 align:middle line:84%
We were sitting right in the
car right outside the door.

00:48:32.190 --> 00:48:34.620 align:middle line:84%
And then one of the cops
came over with a racial slur

00:48:34.620 --> 00:48:36.420 align:middle line:84%
and said, no, it's
this one down here,

00:48:36.420 --> 00:48:38.840 align:middle line:84%
and they just got
up and walked away.

00:48:38.840 --> 00:48:40.703 align:middle line:84%
So this is,
unfortunately, something

00:48:40.703 --> 00:48:41.620 align:middle line:90%
that I had to witness.

00:48:41.620 --> 00:48:43.650 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: How do you
deal with that inside?

00:48:43.650 --> 00:48:45.330 align:middle line:84%
How can you deal
with that injustice?

00:48:45.330 --> 00:48:46.705 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: You
know, it's so tough

00:48:46.705 --> 00:48:49.920 align:middle line:90%
because it's an internal battle.

00:48:49.920 --> 00:48:52.140 align:middle line:84%
You want to cry out,
but there's nobody

00:48:52.140 --> 00:48:55.080 align:middle line:84%
