is on Facebook, over 100,000

00:49:01.480 --> 00:49:02.280 align:middle line:90%
people on that one.

00:49:02.280 --> 00:49:04.440 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Wow, and what
is the mission statement?

00:49:04.440 --> 00:49:07.320 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: It's really
just about exposing

00:49:07.320 --> 00:49:09.510 align:middle line:84%
police brutality,
and police injustice,

00:49:09.510 --> 00:49:11.860 align:middle line:84%
and all different types of
other injustices as well.

00:49:11.860 --> 00:49:15.680 align:middle line:84%
Now, it's kind of grown
and just not saying that--

00:49:15.680 --> 00:49:17.430 align:middle line:84%
not pounding them and
saying, this is evil

00:49:17.430 --> 00:49:19.500 align:middle line:84%
or these people are all
bad, but saying, this

00:49:19.500 --> 00:49:20.550 align:middle line:90%
