These are actual video
accounts of things.

00:49:23.460 --> 00:49:25.002 align:middle line:84%
And I don't add any
extra commentary.

00:49:25.002 --> 00:49:26.550 align:middle line:84%
I don't have any
extra caption to it.

00:49:26.550 --> 00:49:26.617 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:49:26.617 --> 00:49:28.110 align:middle line:90%
Let that speak for itself.

00:49:28.110 --> 00:49:30.932 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: I put it out there,
and I just walk away from it.

00:49:30.932 --> 00:49:32.640 align:middle line:84%
But you can see that
the majority-- and I

00:49:32.640 --> 00:49:35.700 align:middle line:84%
do all races of brutality,
whoever they attack,

00:49:35.700 --> 00:49:38.125 align:middle line:84%
even black people
attacking black people.

00:49:38.125 --> 00:49:39.000 align:middle line:90%
They're all on there.

00:49:39.000 --> 00:49:42.150 align:middle line:84%
But you get to see this track
record of, unfortunately,

00:49:42.150 --> 00:49:46.590 align:middle line:84%
