the balance is off.

00:49:46.590 --> 00:49:49.928 align:middle line:84%
And it's still persisting
to this current day.

00:49:49.928 --> 00:49:51.220 align:middle line:90%
And something needs to be done.

00:49:51.220 --> 00:49:54.510 align:middle line:84%
And I think the best way to
handle it is to get the sheriff

00:49:54.510 --> 00:49:57.570 align:middle line:84%
or the mayor of the town that is
hiring the police officers that

00:49:57.570 --> 00:50:02.040 align:middle line:84%
