and after what they

00:50:19.308 --> 00:50:20.742 align:middle line:90%
did to his brain and his back.

00:50:20.742 --> 00:50:22.200 align:middle line:84%
After it happened,
I said they just

00:50:22.200 --> 00:50:23.950 align:middle line:84%
took 15 years of my
dad's life, and that's

00:50:23.950 --> 00:50:28.020 align:middle line:84%
