00:50:39.690 --> 00:50:40.410 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:50:40.410 --> 00:50:41.850 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: And
until that happens,

00:50:41.850 --> 00:50:43.440 align:middle line:84%
