mystery school teachings

00:52:20.160 --> 00:52:22.810 align:middle line:10%
that you particularly
appreciate or embody.

00:52:22.810 --> 00:52:25.050 align:middle line:84%
>>CARSON: Yeah, well, I
like to talk to people a lot

00:52:25.050 --> 00:52:27.998 align:middle line:84%
about the fact that we are
extremely powerful beings.

00:52:27.998 --> 00:52:29.790 align:middle line:84%
And people don't really
understand how much

00:52:29.790 --> 00:52:31.590 align:middle line:90%
power is inside the human body.

00:52:31.590 --> 00:52:35.530 align:middle line:84%
You have 0.7 milli volts of
electricity in every cell,

00:52:35.530 --> 00:52:37.597 align:middle line:90%
and you have 35 billion cells.

00:52:37.597 --> 00:52:39.180 align:middle line:84%
Multiply that, all
of a sudden, you're

00:52:39.180 --> 00:52:43.838 align:middle line:84%
at 2.65 or so trillion volts of
electricity in the human body.

00:52:43.838 --> 00:52:44.880 align:middle line:90%
So we're powerful beings.

00:52:44.880 --> 00:52:48.510 align:middle line:84%
This is where qigong comes from,
the ancient art of extracting

00:52:48.510 --> 00:52:50.887 align:middle line:84%
the energy and using
it in your hands

00:52:50.887 --> 00:52:52.470 align:middle line:84%
and Reiki healing
and everything else.

00:52:52.470 --> 00:52:54.090 align:middle line:84%
All that energy
is coming directly

00:52:54.090 --> 00:52:57.510 align:middle line:84%
from the cells in the body,
directly from the cell walls.

00:52:57.510 --> 00:52:59.120 align:middle line:90%
And even the ancient Egyptians--

00:52:59.120 --> 00:53:00.510 align:middle line:84%
and if you go into
the mysteries,

00:53:00.510 --> 00:53:02.052 align:middle line:84%
you discover they
have the capability

00:53:02.052 --> 00:53:04.532 align:middle line:84%
of healing with the hands as
well and using these energies.

00:53:04.532 --> 00:53:05.740 align:middle line:90%
So I like to talk about that.

00:53:05.740 --> 00:53:07.800 align:middle line:84%
And I also like to
talk about the fact

00:53:07.800 --> 00:53:10.110 align:middle line:84%
that everything in this
universe is made of light.

00:53:10.110 --> 00:53:11.527 align:middle line:84%
Even our bodies
are made of light.

00:53:11.527 --> 00:53:13.657 align:middle line:84%
When you look at
quantum physics,

00:53:13.657 --> 00:53:15.990 align:middle line:84%
you discover that everything
is an electromagnetic wave.

00:53:15.990 --> 00:53:17.310 align:middle line:90%
Everything is a wave.

00:53:17.310 --> 00:53:19.440 align:middle line:90%
And waves are all light waves.

00:53:19.440 --> 00:53:21.450 align:middle line:90%
We only see 1% of the spectrum.

00:53:21.450 --> 00:53:23.880 align:middle line:84%
We're basically blind to what's
really going on around us.

00:53:23.880 --> 00:53:24.680 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Right.

00:53:24.680 --> 00:53:28.140 align:middle line:84%
